= Widget Order Form =

== Requirements ==

* PHP 5.3+ (tested on 5.5.9)
* MySQL 5.5+ (tested on 5.5.37)

== Installation ==

# Create database from <code>doc/database.sql</code>.
# Deploy files to webserver.
# Create <code>cfg/cfg.custom.php</code> using <code>cfg/cfg.default.php</code> as a model.
# Visit the index page in a Web browser.
# Commence ordering of widgets!
